0:25.000Z","msg":"半年前自己一個去過<br />\nMoscow Saint Petersburg Murmansk<br />\n唔識俄文唔大問題<br />\n大部份年青人都識啲英文<br />\n點都會搵到人幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f94475b626701f2adf02d26227a6c5ad0899e31","tid":225011,"uid":75439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:42:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打試過火車遊由北京出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475c24d53d2d5f01ee7d76bbad12c5b9e1bdb940","tid":225011,"uid":21523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T11:01:45.000Z","msg":"依加係莫斯科，覺得無咩大問題，啲野幾平，平過香港小小添，你預啲人唔識英文同唔會點理你，最好上網睇定交通先，同學定你好，多謝呢啲簡單字，識講小小，啲人即刻無咁西面"},{"pid":"b949683edebf732d90985d922242dc7c2c106886","tid":225011,"uid":27669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴打試過火車遊由北京出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西伯利亞鐵路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  12月"},{"pid":"b5cf1c84e55843f9a3011ab321c58edf8d209d68","tid":225011,"uid":93135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T14:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba08772a8bd51642ffb8ed3630f0b467f6850985","tid":225011,"uid":67676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:26:36.000Z","msg":"全程google translate就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都要搞一輪 因為佢地真係識英文單字<br />\n我去左13日用左15k左右"},{"pid":"9943b5fdb8e5bc992d7354552904e6428442c9c5","tid":225011,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:32:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全程google translate就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都要搞一輪 因為佢地真係識英文單字<br />\n我去左13日用左15k左右</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你譯俄文俾佢咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n俄英雙向直接語音翻譯又得。<br />\n<br />\n前提要上到網"},{"pid":"5a802ddf35ff7b64431a7e3c12c34efe5b998fb3","tid":225011,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:58:28.000Z","msg":"去過四次<br />\n<br />\n莫斯科<br />\n聖彼得堡<br />\n海參崴<br />\n伊爾庫次克<br />\n羅斯托夫～金環<br />\nRostov-On-Don<br />\n加里寧格勒<br />\n喀山<br />\n<br />\n大路城市景點唔難，普通城市難少少，陸路出入境，隨時成個海關冇人識英文。<br />\n<br />\n入境時張出入境紙好有用，搭長途車買車票，酒店住宿，買電話卡，俄羅斯人都會拎佢嚟睇你個名嘅俄文寫法。<br />\n<br />\n免簽証入境嘅話，有一句入住酒店好重要就係 &quot;No Visa&quot; ，最好識埋俄文點讀。<br />\n<br />\n有細陸路出入境關卡係要自己填出入境紙。<br />\n<br />\n自己填番香港，終於唔洗俾人當支那啦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rzdni2fe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frzdni2fe&h=3a3bb4f8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}